ois" lang="cy" hreflang="cy" class="interlanguage-link-target">Cymraeg</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-da"><a href="https://da.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milton_Friedman" title="Milton Friedman — danois" lang="da" hreflang="da" class="interlanguage-link-target">Dansk</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-de"><a href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milton_Friedman" title="Milton Friedman — allemand" lang="de" hreflang="de" class="interlanguage-link-target">Deutsch</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-el"><a href="https://el.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CE%9C%CE%AF%CE%BB%CF%84%CE%BF%CE%BD_%CE%A6%CF%81%CE%AF%CE%BD%CF%84%CE%BC%CE%B1%CE%BD" title="Μίλτον Φρίντμαν — grec" lang="el" hreflang="el" class="interlanguage-link-target">Ελληνικά</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-en badge-Q17437798 badge-goodarticle" title="bon article"><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milton_Friedman" title="Milton Friedman — anglais" lang="en" hreflang="en" class="interlanguage-link-target">English</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-eo"><a href="https://eo.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milton_Friedman" title="Milton Friedman — espéranto" lang="eo" hreflang="eo" class="interlanguage-link-target">Esperanto</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-es"><a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milton_Friedman" title="Milton Friedman — espagnol" lang="es" hreflang="es" class="interlanguage-link-target">Español</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-et"><a href="https://et.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milton_Friedman" title="Milton Friedman — estonien" lang="et" hreflang="et" class="interlanguage-link-target">Eesti</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-eu"><a href="https://eu.wikipedia.org/wiki/Milton_Friedman" title="Milton Friedman — basque" lang="eu" hreflang="eu" class="interlanguage-link-target">Euskara</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-fa"><a href="https://fa.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D9%85%DB%8C%D9%84%D8%AA%D9%88%D9%86_%D9%81%D8%B1%D